  "body": "I instrumented Ganache to track RPC calls per migations (1 contract, 2 contracts, 3 contracts ... 25 contracts) and observed Truffle called `eth_estimateGas` twice per contract.\r\n\r\n|Num Contracts | eth_estimateGas|\r\n|-- | --|\r\n| 1 | 2 |\r\n| 2 | 4 |\r\n| 3 | 6 |\r\n| ... | ... |\r\n| 24 | 48 |\r\n| 25 | 50 |\r\n<img width=\"544\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2529600/174102595-898190ef-5876-41cb-9041-d658fd248ec1.png\">\r\n",
