    "body": "Testing this on the metacoin box I found that there were 5 calls for gas estimation (I checked in @truffle/contract's `getGasEstimate` function so is possible that it is being called from web3 separately?). It turns out that 3 were for the contract deployments. The other 2 I believe were for the transactions that call `setCompleted` on the `Migrations` contract. I deleted the `Migrations` contract and its associated migration file and there were only 3 calls for gas estimation.",
